      "text": [
        " : فِي تُجَّارٍ قَدِمُوا أَرْضاً وَ اِشْتَرَكُوا عَلَى أَنْ لاَ يَبِيعُوا بَيْعَهُمْ إِلاَّ بِمَا أَحَبُّوا قَالَ \"لاَ بَأْسَ بِذَلِكَ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3958 - Al-Nadr narrated from Abdullah ibn Sinan that Abu Abdullah (as), said regarding merchants who arrived at a land and agreed among themselves not to sell their goods except at a price they desired: \"There is no harm in that.\""
